			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "* Have at least 2 characters in your party.\r\n* goto -542; 27; 464, approach Philomeen with the 1 character\r\n* While that character is in the dialog, approach the runepowder barrel (next to her) with another character.\r\n* She will drop her dialog and will play this AD, then explode."
