				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "* The idea: \"I told you not another step forward, but another of yours sneaks in!\"\r\n* Philomeen is playing this AD right before exploding the runepowder barrel, if another player approaches it while she is in her normal dialog (UND_PanicRoom_HiddenGnome).\r\n* This AD is supposed to be short but clear."
